Dirang.title: Dirang
Dirang.byline: Dirang is a town in West Kameng district of Arunachal Pradesh, lying on the floor of a low valley between the higher mountain towns Bomdila and Tawang.

Dire Dawa.title: Dire Dawa
Dire Dawa.byline: Dire Dawa in eastern Ethiopia is one of the country's two chartered cities.
